{
  "texts": [
    "The \"Weserport\" located in Bremen is used for handling steel coils and other break bulk or general cargo.",
    "Overall, it may be considered a small specialized port.",
    "The implementation of the digital twin focuses on precise positioning with a satellitebased system triangulated with position data from a base station installed directly on the terminal.",
    "This data, accurate to a maximum deviation of three centimeters in all directions, is combined with proximity sensors installed on all forklifts and can be used to detect if something is picked up and where the picked-up object is subsequently located (Fig. 5).",
    "The result of this implementation is an automatic data sharing of all operations to the TOS and a live visualization of current operations."
  ]
}